==English==

===Etymology===
Possibly a shortening of {{m|en|[[attractor]] [[beam]]}}; note however the broader meaning of {{m|en|tractor|gloss=machinery that pulls something}}. Coined by [[w:E. E. Smith|E. E. "Doc" Smith]] in his 1931 novel ''[[wikipedia:Spacehounds of IPC|Spacehounds of IPC]]'', first serialised in ''Amaazing Stories''.

